<HEAD>White House Spokesman Denies Existence of Covert Operations Pact</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Subs pvs 7th graf, ``The Post,'' with 5 grafs to expand on
Congress not told of any agreement; picks up pvs 8th graf, ``Asked
